  "detailed_description": "<h1>Add to wishlist!</h1><p></p><br><h1>Check other games:</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594400/extras/1b0f1cd51c0cbf09c2f002ea859e8c06.poster.avif?t=1728829839\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594400/extras/1b0f1cd51c0cbf09c2f002ea859e8c06.webm?t=1728829839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594400/extras/1b0f1cd51c0cbf09c2f002ea859e8c06.mp4?t=1728829839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the <strong>GAI Stops Auto</strong> you will become a traffic police officer. Stop cars and check for violations. You can communicate with drivers in different ways. Write out fines for drivers or take a bribe - it's up to you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Events</strong></h2>Sometimes unpredictable events will occur around you. You must be willing to overcome them. Watch out for the police boss. Beware of wild muscular guys and animals! Explore the space around. Find secret objects.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594400/extras/6f23f875ace8c72ee86e957947234c27.poster.avif?t=1728829839\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594400/extras/6f23f875ace8c72ee86e957947234c27.webm?t=1728829839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594400/extras/6f23f875ace8c72ee86e957947234c27.mp4?t=1728829839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2>Complete the missions and go through the story of a police officer. Reach the end and find out how it all ends!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594400/extras/004fe0c4273e73b7d5a18b9151d1ecca.avif?t=1728829839\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Car traffic system<br></li><li>Dialogs<br></li><li>Epic story<br></li><li>Meme characters<br></li><li>Fun events</li></ul>",
