ps://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594400/extras/004fe0c4273e73b7d5a18b9151d1ecca.avif?t=1728829839\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Car traffic system<br></li><li>Dialogs<br></li><li>Epic story<br></li><li>Meme characters<br></li><li>Fun events</li></ul>",
